data.name: label4.Text
data.value: NOTE: - If you have a problem where you can't see your character, REGENERATE YOUR PLAYER ID THEN REJOIN THE SERVER. - If you tried to connect to the server and you get an error, REJOIN THE SERVER. - To reset your character, type !!!reset into chat. - Your tripcode will only be seen by you and the server host of any server you join. It is used to verify that you are a unique player.
